# Frontend (Next.js)

- **App Router:** `frontend/src/app/` — layout, dashboard (page.tsx), login, register, employees (list, new, [id], [id]/edit), companies, salary, activity, users, settings.
- **API client:** `frontend/src/lib/api.ts` — base URL from `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`, Bearer token from localStorage, fetcher and typed endpoints.
- **Components and types:** `frontend/src/components/`, `frontend/src/types/` — use existing patterns (React Query, React Hook Form + Zod, shadcn/ui).
- **Build:** `frontend/package.json` — `next dev`, `next build`, `next start`.

Routes, features, and API usage are documented in [PROJECT_ANALYSIS.md](PROJECT_ANALYSIS.md) (sections 3, 4, 7). Keep API calls aligned with backend routes in `backend/cmd/api/main.go`. CONTEXT/ is legacy; prefer PROJECT_ANALYSIS and existing frontend code.
